The Ministry of Food and Drug Safety
contacted the person in charge.

00:01:19.589 --> 00:01:20.938
Didn't you hear?

00:01:20.938 --> 00:01:22.605
I wasn't informed...

00:01:22.605 --> 00:01:24.705
Hey, Manager Jang!

00:01:31.205 --> 00:01:33.838
Everyone out, except Manager Jang.

00:01:37.738 --> 00:01:40.105
Didn't you hear what I just said?

00:01:40.105 --> 00:01:41.438
Are you not leaving?

00:01:41.438 --> 00:01:43.705
Let's move. Please step outside.

00:01:43.705 --> 00:01:46.038
Yes, let's go out.

00:01:46.038 --> 00:01:48.184
Team Leader Bang.

00:01:48.184 --> 00:01:49.505
Yeah, yeah.

00:01:49.505 --> 00:01:51.205
Please leave.

00:02:02.605 --> 00:02:04.738
How on earth are you handling your work?

00:02:04.738 --> 00:02:07.838
Does it make sense that the person
in charge found out later than me?

