the problem and prepared countermeasures.

00:02:26.205 --> 00:02:29.705
I'm sorry. I'll go check immediately.

00:02:29.705 --> 00:02:32.805
Do you think I came all this way
just to hear you apologize?

00:02:32.805 --> 00:02:36.472
If this project fails again, will you
take responsibility, Manager Jang?

00:02:38.338 --> 00:02:39.638
President.

00:02:39.638 --> 00:02:42.272
Quiet! You hear me?

00:02:42.272 --> 00:02:43.538
What should we do?

00:02:43.538 --> 00:02:45.305
Is it okay to leave
Manager Jang alone like that?

00:02:45.305 --> 00:02:46.935
- Yeah, I've never seen the President
- Fix it!

00:02:46.935 --> 00:02:48.138
that angry before.

00:02:48.138 --> 00:02:49.349
- Someone should go calm him down.
- Unacceptable!

00:02:49.349 --> 00:02:50.472
It looks like she's taking
all the blame alone.

00:02:50.472 --> 00:02:51.505
Right.

00:02:51.505 --> 00:02:53.905
She took full responsibility
to protect our team.

00:02:53.905 --> 00:02:56.438
- What am I supposed to do?
- If you made a mistake, you must apologize.

00:02:56.438 --> 00:02:57.938
Well...

00:02:57.938 --> 00:02:58.972
Be quiet.

00:02:58.972 --> 00:03:00.572
Team Leader, are you really
just going to sit and watch?

00:03:00.572 --> 00:03:01.972
Manager Nah, why don't you say something?

00:03:01.972 --> 00:03:03.405
Okay, fine. I'll go say something.

00:03:03.405 --> 00:03:05.138
I really can't stand things like this.

00:03:05.138 --> 00:03:06.872
Here we go again.

00:03:06.872 --> 00:03:09.072
President?

00:03:21.172 --> 00:03:23.005
Are you okay?

00:03:23.005 --> 00:03:24.138
Why was he shouting like that?

00:03:24.138 --> 00:03:27.372
I'm really fine, so you can get back to work.

00:03:27.372 --> 00:03:29.005
Are you sure you're okay?

00:03:29.005 --> 00:03:31.672
Wasn't the President being a bit too harsh?

00:03:31.672 --> 00:03:33.861
I thought the glass was going to shatter.

00:03:33.861 --> 00:03:35.172
Oh.

00:03:35.172 --> 00:03:36.505
So that's why he came by?

00:03:36.505 --> 00:03:39.738
