00:07:14.372 --> 00:07:15.438
Du Jun.

00:07:15.438 --> 00:07:17.538
You're not in a position
to worry about anyone right now.

00:07:17.538 --> 00:07:19.238
Right now...

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.105
Oh.

00:07:22.105 --> 00:07:23.805
Chairman.

00:07:30.672 --> 00:07:32.438
What happened?

00:07:32.438 --> 00:07:34.972
What did you do for that article to come out?

00:07:34.972 --> 00:07:36.872
I'm sorry.

00:07:36.872 --> 00:07:38.305
It's not something to apologize for.

00:07:38.305 --> 00:07:41.105
It's all fabricated anyway.

00:07:44.305 --> 00:07:46.305
Why aren't you answering?

00:07:47.605 --> 00:07:50.372
Some of it is true.

00:07:50.372 --> 00:07:52.372
There's a woman I love,

00:07:52.372 --> 00:07:55.672
and she's carrying my child.

00:07:58.138 --> 00:08:01.238
Was all that fuss about not getting married
because of that woman?

00:08:01.238 --> 00:08:03.072
- That's not it, but...
- So,

00:08:03.072 --> 00:08:06.305
the rumor that she's
a company employee is true?

00:08:06.305 --> 00:08:07.605
She is an employee,

00:08:07.605 --> 00:08:09.705
but what the article says is ridiculous.

00:08:09.705 --> 00:08:13.905
It was never a coercive relationship,
and I never told her to get rid of the baby.

00:08:22.405 --> 00:08:24.438
Then this

00:08:24.438 --> 00:08:27.572
has nothing to do with you.

00:08:27.572 --> 00:08:29.572
- What?
- For now, that's how it has to be.

00:08:29.572 --> 00:08:31.572
There is no such woman or child.

00:08:31.572 --> 00:08:34.872
Set up an interview immediately
and say it's completely false.

00:08:34.872 --> 00:08:37.738
Announce strong legal action for defamation.

00:08:37.738 --> 00:08:38.772
But Father...

00:08:38.772 --> 00:08:40.738
We need to stabilize the stock price first.

00:08:40.738 --> 00:08:42.638
What about the company's image?

00:08:43.372 --> 00:08:46.405
The truth can be set straight later.

00:08:46.405 --> 00:08:47.505
When is 'later'?

00:08:47.505 --> 00:08:50.205
If I deny everything to save myself,
she'll have to give birth in hiding,

00:08:50.205 --> 00:08:51.877
without anyone knowing who the father is.

00:08:51.877 --> 00:08:53.605
Is that what you want me to do?

00:08:53.605 --> 00:08:54.638
I can't do that.

00:08:54.638 --> 00:08:56.905
Right now, you're not just one woman's man.

00:08:56.905 --> 00:08:58.605
You're the owner of a company.

00:08:58.605 --> 00:09:02.438
One word from you affects
the livelihood of thousands.

00:09:02.438 --> 00:09:04.738
You know who's behind this, don't you?

00:09:04.738 --> 00:09:08.138
Your sister-in-law is waiting
for you to make a mistake.

00:09:08.138 --> 00:09:12.572
The moment you acknowledge that woman,
it becomes the excuse to bring you down.

00:09:16.972 --> 00:09:18.938
For now, do as I say.

00:09:18.938 --> 00:09:22.238
Because that's the way
to protect you and her.

00:09:31.005 --> 00:09:33.672
The subscriber's phone is turned off,
please leave a message...

00:09:33.672 --> 00:09:36.172
His phone is still off.

00:09:36.172 --> 00:09:38.205
Is he okay?

00:09:38.205 --> 00:09:40.205
Right, did you see the stock crash yesterday?

00:09:40.205 --> 00:09:42.772
All because of one article
about the President, what a disaster.

00:09:42.772 --> 00:09:43.972
Exactly.

00:09:43.972 --> 00:09:46.672
But that woman who's supposedly pregnant,
is it just me who finds it suspicious?

00:09:46.672 --> 00:09:49.272
I mean she could have done it for the money.

00:09:49.272 --> 00:09:53.238
Right, maybe she deliberately seduced him,
then exposed him when it didn't go her way.

00:09:53.238 --> 00:09:55.077
That's what I'm saying.

00:09:55.077 --> 00:09:57.038
- Oh.
- Morning.

00:09:57.038 --> 00:09:59.305
What do you think, Manager Jang?

00:09:59.305 --> 00:10:01.405
- Pardon?
- You work in a key department.

00:10:01.405 --> 00:10:02.705
Thought you might've heard something.

00:10:02.705 --> 00:10:05.605
Well, I'm not sure.

00:10:12.805 --> 00:10:14.605
Did I see wrong that day?

00:10:14.605 --> 00:10:17.405
- Didn't seem like a forced relationship.
- Listen.

