It's weird. Really weird.

00:10:29.905 --> 00:10:33.305
The location is just too strange, you know.

00:10:34.738 --> 00:10:38.638
Is that article about the President true?

00:10:40.172 --> 00:10:43.372
No, how could it be?

00:10:43.372 --> 00:10:47.269
That he's seeing someone? And she's pregnant?

00:10:47.269 --> 00:10:50.138
Well, that's...

00:10:51.638 --> 00:10:53.505
Ugh, jeez.

00:10:53.505 --> 00:10:54.772
Why is it so dusty in here?

00:10:54.772 --> 00:10:56.205
My throat feels irritated.

00:10:56.205 --> 00:11:00.638
I'm really busy right now,
I'm sorry. I have to go.

00:11:10.872 --> 00:11:13.338
So why did she call us here now?

00:11:13.338 --> 00:11:15.238
I don't know.

00:11:15.238 --> 00:11:17.138
Okay, coffee's here.

00:11:17.138 --> 00:11:22.338
I got iced Americanos for everyone,
so don't drink it if you don't want to.

00:11:22.338 --> 00:11:23.872
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:11:23.872 --> 00:11:24.905
Is this on you, Team Leader?

00:11:24.905 --> 00:11:28.272
Manager Jang, coffee.

00:11:28.272 --> 00:11:32.605
Pardon? I already had coffee
this morning, so I'm fine.

00:11:32.605 --> 00:11:33.872
Whether you drank it or not,

00:11:33.872 --> 00:11:38.505
weren't you used to chugging
grande-sized drinks after lunch?

00:11:38.505 --> 00:11:41.972
Well, then, thank you.

00:11:44.272 --> 00:11:45.305
Be honest with me.

00:11:45.305 --> 00:11:47.938
What's the real reason you can't drink?

00:11:47.938 --> 00:11:50.672
There's one reason
that comes to mind right now.

00:11:50.672 --> 00:11:53.305
