When would she have time with the President?

00:13:03.372 --> 00:13:06.538
You've been watching too many dramas.

00:13:10.841 --> 00:13:12.389
Sorry.

00:13:18.972 --> 00:13:20.505
Thank goodness it didn't get exposed.

00:13:20.505 --> 00:13:22.805
Does Team Leader know something?

00:13:22.805 --> 00:13:25.505
Exactly. We can't ask outright.

00:13:25.505 --> 00:13:28.472
Should I tell the truth?

00:13:28.472 --> 00:13:31.272
Even if you do tell her,
now doesn't feel like the right time.

00:13:31.272 --> 00:13:33.338
The company is too chaotic right now.

00:13:33.338 --> 00:13:36.838
Okay. I'll be more careful.

00:13:36.838 --> 00:13:38.138
By the way,

00:13:38.138 --> 00:13:40.453
